t."],[4346,4450,"Only the biggest names."],[4521,4575,"Well,"],[4733,4825,"I just so happened"],[4825,5013,"to be a VIP card member here."]],"26":[[112,279,"Our VIP cards are gold."],[279,442,"We don't have black ones."],[442,629,"Well, your boss gave that one to me, so"],[667,825,"are you telling me that he's lying?"],[850,1130,"Why is this disgusting,"],[1130,1434,"filthy janitor lady still lying to me?"],[1434,1580,"Do you even know who my boss is?"],[1580,1697,"As if he'd waste his time with"],[1697,1843,"someone dressed like you."],[1843,2022,"The card really is from your boss."],[2047,2122,"If you don't believe me,"],[2122,2177,"you can ask him"],[2177,2348,"yourself. - Ask him what?"],[2373,2531,"Some janitor having"],[2531,2698,"possession of a VIP card?"],[2756,2831,"Please."],[2869,2965,"Now, get out!"],[2965,3161,"Before I drag you out myself."],[3203,3278,"Grace?"],[3332,3591,"Ah, Mr. Sterling's friend!"],[3591,3707,"Welcome, sir."],[3707,3858,"Did he just call me Grace?"],[3858,3987,"What exactly were you planning on"],[3987,4108,"doing to my old classmate?"],[4166,4471,"Ah, uh, classmate?"],[4500,4612,"Uh, there seems"],[4612,4750,"to be no problem at all, sir."],[4788,5075,"Just a little bit of a misunderstanding."],[5847,5922,"Grace."],[5922,6010,"You used to be one of the"],[6010,6164,"best students in our class."],[6185,6281,"How'd you end up"],[6281,6427,"working as a janitor?"]],"27":[[8,104,"Who are you?"],[166,321,"Come on, don't play dumb."],[350,492,"I asked you out back in high school."],[492,529,"You know,"],[529,654,"if you just would have said yes,"],[654,796,"then you wouldn't have to be"],[855,1005,"stuck doing cleaning work now."],[1046,1201,"He actually thinks I'm Grace."],[1284,1388,"Um."],[1484,1551,"I'm sorry, I-"],[1551,1697,"Listen, we can chat later."],[1697,1772,"Today's actually"],[1772,1922,"our annual class reunion."],[1922,2027,"Whole gang's over there."],[2047,2202,"You should come hang out with us."],[2268,2464,"This could be fun..."],[2627,2694,"This way."],[3069,3157,"Boss!"],[3157,3378,"Some random janitor"],[3378,3586,"tried to pass herself off as a VIP!"],[3603,3703,"A janitor?"],[3762,3958,"She used this."],[4250,4454,"Poor people really are clueless."],[4454,4637,"Our VIP cards are gold."],[4637,4763,"She must have found some"],[4763,4950,"random black card from off the street,"],[4950,5059,"and thought she could-"],[5342,5459,"Where is she?"],[5476,5522,"Boss."],[5522,5676,"The reason you've never seen"],[5676,5772,"seen this black card"],[5772,5914,"is because there's only one of them."],[5955,6214,"Get, go find her, you discriminating idiot."],[6406,6468,"And if you can't,"],[6468,6585,"don't bother coming back!"],[6648,6715,"Yes, sir."],[7115,7257,"I need you to prepare a gift,"],[7257,7353,"and make it big."],[7353,7515,"I want to pay my respects"],[7515,7657,"to a very important guest."]],"28":[[154,246,"Hey guys."],[308,400,"Look who I brought."],[437,558,"Are you kidding me, Kevin?"],[558,725,"You seriously invited a janitor"],[725,821,"to our student reunion?"],[821,984,"No, guys, she's-"],[984,1113,"Oh, whatever."],[1113,1184,"Now that you're here,"],[1184,1322,"make yourself useful."],[1322,1547,"My car could use a good scrubbing."],[1630,1710,"Go wash it."],[1914,2056,"I'm sorry, are you talking to me?"],[2127,2264,"Oh, I, I don't see anyone else"],[2264,2419,"who cleans stuff for a living here."],[2419,2635,"I'm sorry, I don't clean for-"],[2635,2844,"Okay, less talking, more action."],[2844,3032,"Oh, and careful with my car,"],[3032,3274,"it's worth more than your entire life."],[3303,3478,"If you scratch it, I'll skin you alive."],[3545,3599,"Miss, I think you"],[3599,3720,"might have me mistaken for-"],[3720,3782,"For what?"],[3803,3841,"Do you see"],[3841,3949,"what the fuck you're wearing?"],[4020,4237,"Oh, I get it."],[4237,4525,"You want money, paper, mulah."],[4583,4742,"You poor folks are all the same."],[4917,4992,"Jesus."],[5630,5705,"Oh."],[5776,5864,"There you go."],[5901,5976,"Take it."],[5976,6072,"Get to work."]],"29":[[12,279,"No, Stella, you've really got it wrong."],[300,396,"Look closer."],[429,604,"Don't you recognize her?"],[696,913,"All I see is a raggedy,"],[913,1042,"food-stamp-using bitch."],[1042,1121,"Seriously?"],[1121,1288,"Oh my God, Stella."],[1301,1459,"She's our old classmate."],[1564,1647,"Grace?"],[1664,1780,"Is that really you?"],[1780,1826,"I'm not-"],[1826,1935,"Yes, it's her."],[1935,2039,"She's Grace."],[2039,2239,"It is really you."],[2239,2314,"Wait, wait, wait."],[2314,2544,"I heard you were California's hottest"],[2544,2773,"up-and-coming business prodigy."],[2790,2952,"How did you sink to this?"],[2952,3103,"Wow, these people really"],[3103,3269,"have no idea who I am."],[3269,3453,"They actually think I'm my sister."],[3453,3570,"Oh, you haven't heard?"],[3570,3712,"Grace's company collapsed."],[3712,3866,"Her whole staff jumped ship."],[3866,3958,"No freaking way."],[3958,4012,"When?"],[4012,4149,"Just this morning."],[4170,4371,"She got totally crushed by my aunt,"],[4371,4491,"and her husband's company."],[4491,4633,"My cousin even called me and"],[4633,4804,"told me to teach Grace a lesson."],[4863,4963,"Looks like she's already"],[4963,5080,"hit rock bottom, though."],[5080,5155,"Your cousin?"],[5155,5347,"Yeah, Eva."],[5388,5613,"This is what you get, Grace."],[5647,5730,"It's karma"],[5730,5889,"for trying to steal her boyfriend."],[5889,6026,"Any decent woman your age"],[6026,6210,"would be looking for a good husband."],[6210,6289,"But not you."],[6310,6502,"You're too busy trying to play"],[6502,6673,"the home-wrecking mistress!"],[6698,6844,"I stole her boyfriend?"],[6956,7127,"I'm a home-wrecking mistress?"]],"30":[[33,166,"Did you really do that?"],[187,296,"Grace didn't do anything."],[296,404,"This is all slander."],[404,487,"Slander?"],[487,546,"What?"],[604,750,"Got caught in the act and"],[750,917,"now you're afraid to come clean?"],[934,1101,"Actually, you've got this all backwards."],[1134,1259,"The only person here who"],[1259,1497,"wormed into Grace's boyfriend's"],[1497,1680,"bedroom is your cousin."],[1680,1826,"Don't you dare speak about"],[1826,1989,"my cousin like that, Grace!"],[1989,2131,"Fucking another girl's man,"],[2131,2264,"and acting all innocent?"],[2302,2456,"Grace, when did you"],[2456,2627,"become so shameless?"],[2627,2748,"I'm just speaking facts."],[2748,2915,"If Eva is so in love with that manwhore,"],[2915,3032,"she can have him."],[3032,3119,"He's not exactly what we"],[3119,3253,"would call a catch."],[3278,3328,"Plus,"],[3415,3561,"Grace already has a new boyfriend."],[3578,3741,"Please, what type of guy would wanna"],[3741,3895,"date someone dressed like that?"],[3928,3995,"Grace,"],[4016,4120,"you don't have to come in here,"],[4120,4254,"and act all weird referring"],[4254,4412,"to yourself in the third person."],[4458,4658,"We're old classmates."],[4675,4829,"You can be honest with us."],[4846,4975,"I am being honest."],[5125,5255,"Grace has almost made it official"],[5255,5372,"with her new boyfriend,"],[5413,5509,"Thomas Cohen."],[5509,5609,"Thomas Cohen?"],[5609,5801,"Like that Thomas Cohen?"],[5922,6101,"Jesus, Grace, what are you smoking?"],[6143,6277,"Thomas Cohen is the most"],[6277,6498,"eligible bachelor in California."],[6523,6606,"He wouldn't be caught"],[6606,6698,"dead with you."],[6710,6781,"I mean, come on,"],[6781,6940,"how delusional can you be?"],[6956,7061,"You're not even good enough to"],[7061,7132,"go out with the guy"],[7132,7273,"that mows Thomas Cohen's lawn."],[7273,7536,"Grace, just drop the act already."],[7570,7761,"If anything you said was actually true,"],[7761,7849,"you wouldn't walk in here"],[7849,7974,"dressed like a janitor."],[8003,8128,"If you wanna fact-check me,"],[8128,8220,"you should call your cousin."],[8249,8316,"Fine."],[8345,8479,"I'll call her up right now."],[8525,8650,"Let's see how smug you look"],[8650,8854,"after she exposes your ass."]],"31":[[825,959,"Eva and her family's company"],[959,1059,"just went bankrupt."],[1059,1155,"They're already in debt with"],[1155,1251,"multiple suppliers,"],[1251,1484,"so my guess would be"],[1484,1605,"that they're too busy dealing with"],[1605,1772,"their complaints to answer the phone."],[1772,2010,"God, you're so full of shit, Grace."],[2047,2285,"That kind of info is reserved"],[2285,2419,"for business insiders,"],[2431,2631,"not no-name toilet cleaners."],[2631,2740,"Well, this outfit isn't"],[2740,2827,"for cleaning toilets."],[2827,2961,"Alright, alright."],[2965,3144,"Why don't we just tone it down, yeah?"],[3157,3265,"This is a high school reunion,"],[3265,3353,"we should be reminiscing"],[3353,3445,"on the past."],[3461,3645,"After all, we have a lot to talk about"],[3645,3762,"since high school, right?"],[3778,3874,"Come on, let's sit."],[4208,4304,"We really do."],[4333,4462,"Guys, remember how Grace"],[4462,4537,"got good grades?"],[4537,4662,"But when it came to everything else,"],[4662,4833,"she was totally useless?"],[4833,5005,"You always went on and on"],[5005,5109,"about your sister,"],[5109,5321,"and how you wanted to make her proud,"],[5321,5413,"and repay her"],[5413,5551,"for covering your tuition?"],[5551,5709,"Oh, look at you now."],[5709,5918,"You spent all that time studying and"],[5960,6143,"now you sweep up trash for a living."],[6143,6252,"So you look down on me,"],[6252,6356,"because I'm a janitor?"],[6373,6418,"Sure."],[6439,6619,"Janitors are blue-collar workers."],[6656,6760,"But they're good people,"],[6760,6852,"and they are just working"],[6852,6948,"to provide for their family"],[6948,7098,"just like the rest of us."],[7144,7286,"So if you were going to judge,"],[7340,7465,"save it for the thieves,"],[7465,7540,"and the drug dealers."],[7540,7728,"You sure yap a lot, don't you?"],[7728,7774,"Tell us,"],[7774,7924,"how much do you make per month?"],[7987,8091,"Probably not enough to"],[8091,8287,"support yourself, let alone a family."],[8287,8366,"You don't deserve the"],[8366,8466,"dignity of knowing."],[8466,8679,"But, I will tell you this."],[9017,9271,"Your entire family's fortune"],[9363,9580,"wouldn't make a dent in my bank account."]],"32":[[0,125,"Oh, please."],[162,342,"You were always going to be a"],[342,600,"worthless, broke bitch."],[625,779,"We used to bully your ass"],[779,984,"in high school every single day,"],[1013,1217,"and you never had the guts to"],[1217,1305,"fight back!"],[1351,1514,"You were the easiest target ever."],[1576,1680,"These people bullied Grace"],[1680,1764,"back in high school?"],[1789,1897,"What are you talking about?"],[1897,2014,"Oh, you don't remember?"],[2068,2285,"Guys, let's help our friend."],[2285,2394,"Jog her memory."],[2456,2623,"Now that everyone thinks I'm Grace,"],[2623,2815,"I might as well keep playing along."],[2831,3007,"Let's find out what these idiots"],[3007,3103,"did to my sister."],[3232,3353,"Cat got me these new shoes"],[3353,3495,"for my birthday!"],[3536,3803,"She is the best sister ever."],[3983,4112,"Did I say you could"],[4112,4245,"talk to my boyfriend?"],[4245,4358,"You skank!"],[4358,4400,"What?"],[4400,4558,"No, he, he was just asking me"],[4558,4671,"about the homework assignment-"],[4671,4842,"I don't give a fuck"],[4917,5013,"what it was about."],[5092,5159,"No!"],[5501,5634,"My sister saved up a whole month"],[5634,5751,"to buy me these!"],[5801,5897,"That's better."],[5897,6160,"Dirty shoes for a dirty slut."],[6281,6343,"Stop!"],[6343,6435,"Let me go!"],[6473,6577,"What are you doing?"],[6644,6690,"Stop!"],[6690,6794,"What are you doing?"],[6856,6994,"Making sure everyone sees you"],[6994,7132,"for the whore you are."],[7132,7340,"No, please, I didn't do anything-"],[7403,7532,"Stop! Help!"],[7578,7699,"Somebody help!"],[7699,7774,"No!"],[8024,8099,"Let's go."],[8116,8179,"Ha!"],[8416,8470,"Cat,"],[8579,8775,"I wish I was as strong as you."],[8925,9280,"Grace, why didn't you tell me?"]],"33":[[25,208,"Alright guys,"],[208,446,"let's not be too harsh on Grace."],[446,579,"We all know her mommy"],[579,804,"and daddy abandoned her."],[817,1001,"It can't have been easy growing up"],[1001,1297,"as a low class, parentless gutter rat."],[1297,1480,"Grace would have been street meat,"],[1480,1630,"if it wasn't for her sister."],[1630,1764,"I mean, that poor girl"],[1764,1931,"worked her butt off,"],[1931,2173,"so that she could provide for them."],[2193,2556,"Oh, remember Grace used to skip meals,"],[2556,2786,"because she felt bad for being a burden?"],[2786,2982,"I mean, even we tried to be nice,"],[2982,3148,"and share our lunch with her."],[3361,3511,"Oh my God, Grace."],[3511,3707,"Is that all you're gonna eat for lunch?"],[3707,3845,"I know you and your sister"],[3845,4091,"can't afford the cafeteria food, so"],[4212,4366,"we wanted to help you out."],[4366,4412,"Stop."],[4412,4483,"What are you doing?"],[4483,4571,"Let me go!"],[4571,4617,"Stop!"],[4692,4729,"Stop!"],[4729,4850,"Let me go!"],[4946,5021,"No!"],[5146,5271,"No, please!"],[5626,5830,"Broke, orphan bitch."],[5830,5939,"We gave you a free lunch and"],[5939,6114,"you don't even thank us?"],[6114,6214,"Lap it up."],[6214,6297,"Now!"],[6356,6456,"Unless,"],[6589,6748,"you want some desserts too."],[7165,7353,"I can't tell Cat about them."],[7353,7503,"She has enough to worry about."],[7595,7678,"Huh."],[7703,7916,"I wonder what Grace's sister"],[7916,8053,"is up to these days."],[8053,8195,"Oh, who knows?"],[8241,8495,"Maybe she's a janitor too now."]],"34":[[4,266,"Wow, two janitors in one family?"],[266,396,"What a dynamic duo!"],[500,563,"Grace,"],[596,750,"don't hold the past against them."],[750,946,"I mean, you know how high school is."],[946,1063,"Kids always playing"],[1063,1197,"pranks on each other and stuff."],[1197,1338,"So those were just pranks?"],[1338,1443,"No, I just"],[1443,1614,"meant that it's all behind us now."],[1643,1705,"You turned out pretty good"],[1705,1801,"all things considered."],[1810,1889,"You're right."],[1922,2035,"I did turn out much better"],[2035,2168,"than these ignorant scums did."],[2206,2264,"I mean,"],[2302,2456,"I guess it's true what they say."],[2548,2681,"Bullies only peak in high school."],[2681,2836,"What did you just call us?"],[2836,2907,"You heard me."],[2990,3119,"You fools shouldn't even be able to"],[3119,3199,"breathe the same air"],[3199,3328,"as someone like Grace."],[3328,3432,"You little-"],[3699,3778,"See this?"],[3778,3870,"Eva's calling."],[3870,4091,"You're so fucking busted, Grace."]],"35":[[262,554,"You are so fucking busted, Grace."],[771,938,"See you soon, Eva."],[938,1172,"Eva's on her way as we speak."],[1192,1305,"So if I were you,"],[1347,1484,"I'd fess up with your lies"],[1484,1568,"while you still can."],[1601,1789,"You don't wanna see my cousin"],[1789,1897,"when she's mad."],[2002,2110,"I assure you,"],[2110,2260,"all of these little lies will be cleared up"],[2260,2373,"as soon as Eva arrives."],[2373,2510,"God, you're really doubling down"],[2510,2681,"your bullshit, aren't you?"],[2736,2827,"Come on, guys."],[2873,2986,"What is it worth fighting"],[2986,3144,"with a toilet-scrubber?"],[3178,3365,"We all know how poor people are."],[3436,3511,"All talk."],[3586,3682,"They've never had money,"],[3682,3812,"so words are their only weapon."],[4108,4279,"Words are my only weapon?"],[4383,4471,"You so sure about that-"],[4471,4533,"Grace,"],[4587,4692,"do you really have to make"],[4692,4813,"such a scene here?"],[4896,5005,"I mean, it's clear you're not"],[5005,5134,"whoever you're claiming to be."],[5134,5234,"So could you just"],[5296,5426,"be yourself and move past this?"],[5426,5547,"I've been myself since the moment"],[5547,5655,"I walked through that door."],[5751,5930,"It's you who are accusing me of lying."],[6001,6193,"I'm disappointed in you, Grace."],[6231,6293,"Okay."],[6318,6443,"I mean, in high school,"],[6443,6589,"sure you were short on cash, but"],[6648,6802,"you always had a smile on your face."],[6823,6915,"You were real."],[7011,7169,"And now you're just-"],[7453,7536,"Now I'm what?"],[7615,7678,"Can you just"],[7678,7816,"please stop being so stubborn?"],[7870,7982,"I mean, Stella's dad is the"],[7982,8091,"owner of this hotel."],[8112,8237,"If you just apologize to her"],[8237,8362,"for this whole fiasco,"],[8475,8571,"maybe she could help you"],[8571,8654,"find a job here."],[8654,8783,"Help me find a job here?"],[8825,9009,"Grace, this is one of the top hotels"],[9009,9125,"in the world."],[9159,9284,"What, are you saying you're too good"],[9284,9359,"for this place?"],[9359,9480,"Actually, yes."],[9509,9622,"I am far too good"],[9622,9734,"for your daddy's little hotel."],[9734,9872,"What did you just- - Oh my God!"],[9901,9976,"Eva!"],[9976,10139,"You're finally here!"]],"36":[[4,79,"Eva!"],[79,258,"You're finally here!"],[279,433,"Why the hell did you tell me"],[433,571,"to come all the way up here?"],[629,842,"Don't you know how busy I am?"],[842,1042,"Eva, this is serious."],[1042,1105,"There's someone who's"],[1105,1209,"spewing nonsense about"],[1209,1372,"your company going bankrupt."],[1401,1505,"She even accused you of being"],[1505,1618,"someone's mistress."],[1618,1764,"And just who might that be?"],[1776,1851,"It was her."],[1972,2039,"Grace."],[2819,2952,"Cat got your tongue?"],[3003,3115,"I thought you were gonna"],[3115,3332,"clear things up once Eva arrived."],[3332,3507,"If you knew what was good for you,"],[3536,3770,"you'd get over here and apologize now!"],[4037,4087,"Oh."],[4266,4425,"Ahhh!"],[4617,4688,"Wow."],[4713,4767,"Eva."],[4842,4934,"What did you do that for?"],[4934,5025,"You've been telling her"],[5025,5146,"to apologize to me?"],[5184,5347,"Yeah, so she was"],[5347,5488,"spreading rumors about you."],[5513,5643,"Who the fuck are you"],[5643,5789,"to demand that she apologize to me?"],[5789,5976,"Eva, why are you being like this?"],[6010,6076,"Look,"],[6076,6260,"whatever you used to think about Grace."],[6285,6493,"She's just a filthy janitor now."],[6502,6581,"I mean,"],[6581,6752,"you see what she's wearing, right?"],[6773,6977,"She's a complete fucking joke!"],[7244,7390,"You don't even know who she is!"],[7415,7520,"And you still want her"],[7520,7632,"to apologize to me?"],[7795,8133,"The only joke in this room is you."]],"37":[[500,600,"Who she is?"],[633,738,"Is she not just some"],[738,905,"piss-poor cleaning lady?"],[905,1042,"Ah, Jesus!"],[1092,1234,"You're just as stupid"],[1234,1359,"as you're blind!"],[1726,1914,"Ma'am, I'm so sorry."],[1972,2173,"Uh, it seems that my cousin"],[2173,2339,"didn't recognize you."],[2373,2577,"And I hope that her foolishness"],[2577,2769,"doesn't affect things between us."],[2806,2877,"Eva,"],[2969,3082,"what's gotten into you?"],[3115,3190,"Just this morning,"],[3190,3278,"you were calling Grace"],[3278,3357,"a slutty mistress,"],[3357,3520,"and saying we will teach her a lesson."],[3520,3645,"Shut your fucking mouth."],[3645,3745,"Seriously?"],[3791,3937,"Why are you being like this?"],[3937,4062,"Why are you so afraid of her"],[4062,4145,"all of a sudden?"],[4175,4329,"She's just a fucking"],[4350,4508,"janitor, for fuck's sake!"],[4988,5080,"Oh my God."],[5221,5288,"Stay there,"],[5568,5718,"dont't fucking move."],[6177,6435,"Ma'am, I sincerely hope"],[6435,6589,"that you overlook this"],[6702,6810,"incident."],[6977,7077,"As you can recall,"],[7077,7282,"patience isn't exactly my strong suite."],[7282,7415,"So get your cousin out of here,"],[7415,7540,"before her whining"],[7565,7732,"causes my ear drums to rupture."],[7882,8037,"Yes, right away."],[9017,9180,"What the hell just happened?"],[9392,9463,"Not bad."]],"38":[[70,145,"Not bad."],[271,321,"Huh."],[321,496,"Okay, who are you actually?"],[496,583,"Oh, come on, Kevin."],[583,788,"She's clearly still Gutter Rat Grace."],[788,925,"I mean, who else would she be?"],[925,967,"Seriously,"],[967,1096,"what the hell is wrong with you?"],[1096,1238,"We were nice enough to invite you"],[1238,1338,"for our student reunion,"],[1338,1430,"and you had to go fuck up"],[1430,1534,"the whole day for us."],[1534,1576,"Really?"],[1576,1630,"Ruined?"],[1710,1764,"I was honestly"],[1764,1860,"having a great time myself."],[1860,2018,"Oh, cut the smugness."],[2052,2173,"Whatever scare tactic"],[2173,2281,"you use on Alicia's cousin"],[2281,2427,"is not gonna work on me."],[2489,2623,"You shouldn't forget my father"],[2623,2731,"is the owner of this hotel."],[2731,2781,"And?"],[2781,2890,"Damn it, Grace,"],[2890,3086,"I am trying to give you a chance!"],[3111,3203,"You damn well know"],[3203,3294,"I could have my father"],[3294,3420,"throw you out by now."],[3420,3536,"If your father sees"],[3536,3611,"what's happening here,"],[3611,3782,"the first person he's gonna kick out is"],[3782,3895,"wow, his own daughter."],[4041,4116,"You're so"],[4116,4266,"un-fucking-believable!"],[4571,4750,"That's it, I'm calling my dad right now."]],"39":[[450,638,"Oh, there you are, Thomas."],[717,909,"What a wonderful day this is."],[971,1055,"I never dreamed that"],[1055,1234,"the Warlord Queen herself would"],[1276,1455,"grace my hotel with her presence."],[1514,1626,"And when you see her later,"],[1643,1726,"please do let her know"],[1726,1889,"how much I admire her."],[1889,2018,"I'm sure you've heard of the"],[2018,2156,"Warlord Queen's famous temper."],[2223,2323,"If she finds any faults"],[2323,2427,"in your hotel, then,"],[2460,2573,"won't be much I can do to help you."],[2594,2711,"Is Catherine really"],[2711,2865,"that much of a big shot?"],[2865,2994,"Of couse she is."],[3011,3103,"Well, she's worshipped"],[3103,3282,"like a God here in California!"],[3361,3428,"Not to mention,"],[3428,3566,"if she hadn't saved my ass"],[3566,3691,"back in the day,"],[3691,3753,"I wouldn't have been here"],[3753,3853,"to open this hotel."],[4145,4262,"Oh."],[4491,4675,"Excuse me, I gotta take this."],[5105,5192,"Hey Stella, what's up?"],[5388,5442,"What?"],[5568,5668,"Someone has a nerve to"],[5668,5772,"bully my own daughter"],[5772,5876,"on my own turf?"],[5968,6106,"I'm on my way right now."]],"40":[[4,91,"Thank you, daddy."],[266,321,"Hear that?"],[379,546,"My dad will be here any second."],[583,671,"So if you wanna leave with"],[671,850,"even a shred of dignity,"],[850,1071,"I recommend you scram ASAP."],[1117,1217,"I'm terrified."],[1247,1351,"Grace, just"],[1422,1614,"stop making this a whole big thing."],[1614,1735,"Just apologize to Stella and then"],[1735,1830,"we can all move on."],[1856,2002,"You want me to apologize to her?"],[2027,2072,"What,"],[2072,2227,"you think we're gonna do it for you?"],[2323,2427,"God dammit, Grace,"],[2427,2648,"this class reunion was going perfectly"],[2648,2748,"until you showed up"],[2748,2873,"and turned it to shit."],[2873,3032,"Read the room, Grace."],[3048,3136,"Everyone's telling you"],[3136,3253,"to apologize to Stella."],[3282,3470,"Her dad isn't just some hotel owner,"],[3532,3624,"the guy's got connections"],[3624,3778,"to the freaking Warlord Queen."],[3887,4020,"The Warlord Queen?"],[4020,4158,"You don't even know"],[4158,4350,"who the Warlord Queen is?"],[4450,4679,"You were really live under a rock."],[4679,4884,"She's only the most powerful person"],[4884,4996,"in this country."],[5030,5192,"She runs our special forces."],[5192,5288,"She controls over a"],[5288,5438,"trillion dollars in assets."],[5438,5526,"I mean, heck,"],[5526,5651,"she basically has the President"],[5651,5743,"under her thumb!"],[5964,6193,"Oh, sure laugh."],[6239,6343,"But just wait."],[6406,6602,"My dad and the Warlord Queen"],[6602,6727,"are close friends."],[6727,6831,"So you better hope he doesn't"],[6831,6952,"call her over here."],[7015,7094,"Close friend?"],[7094,7148,"Wow."],[7223,7394,"I probably would've known about that."],[7394,7457,"Why the fuck"],[7457,7582,"would you know of all people?"],[7645,7761,"The Warlord Queen"],[7761,8020,"saved my father's life a while ago."],[8053,8191,"And later she invited him"],[8191,8316,"on a personal tour"],[8316,8512,"of her top-secret bases."],[8646,8708,"You would have to be there"],[8708,8804,"yourself to know."],[8804,8871,"Well,"],[8988,9109,"actually I have."],[9225,9292,"Wait, what?"],[9292,9426,"What the hell are you saying?"]],"41":[[16,79,"Wait, what?"],[79,233,"What the hell are you saying?"],[608,667,"God."],[754,942,"I give you an inch, you take a mile."],[1001,1151,"Grace, you wouldn't even be hired"],[1151,1259,"to clean the shit off the floor"],[1259,1372,"at one of those bases."],[1655,1785,"What, do you think I'm crazy?"],[1931,2093,"That I've lost my marbles?"],[2093,2339,"Grace, just let it go."],[2339,2464,"No one's saying you're crazy."],[2464,2565,"Yeah, because crazy"],[2565,2715,"would be too light of a word!"],[3003,3103,"By the way,"],[3140,3269,"my father promised me"],[3269,3382,"that the next time"],[3382,3557,"he sees the Warlord Queen,"],[3574,3670,"he's gonna arrange for me"],[3670,3828,"to be her personal assistant."],[3870,4037,"I'm gonna be inches away"],[4037,4179,"from greatness."],[4179,4387,"Holy shit, no way."],[4412,4592,"Oh, I can't believe I'm best friends"],[4592,4696,"with the Warlord Queen's"],[4696,4859,"personal assistant."],[4859,4929,"That's like"],[4963,5092,"one degree of separation away"],[5092,5226,"from the Queen herself."],[5263,5351,"The Warlord Queen"],[5351,5497,"keeps it low profile anyway."],[5497,5638,"It's not like anybody can just get"],[5638,5743,"a glimpse of her."],[5768,5818,"Oh!"],[5889,6001,"When you become her assistant,"],[6001,6160,"can you please introduce us?"],[6218,6285,"You do know"],[6285,6385,"who you're going up against,"],[6385,6468,"right, Grace?"],[6468,6602,"Stella's dad has friends"],[6602,6785,"in very high places."]],"42":[[33,162,"Stella's dad."],[1526,1614,"Oh, no."],[1989,2173,"Ma'am, I wanted to thank you in person"],[2173,2323,"for saving my life."],[2323,2477,"I'm eternally indebted to you."],[2594,2748,"If possible, I would like to"],[2748,2848,"arrange for my daughter"],[2848,2969,"to serve as your full-time"],[2969,3090,"personal assistant someday."],[3119,3249,"It's the least my family can do"],[3249,3353,"to repay you."],[3586,3678,"Oh, yeah."],[3712,3858,"No, you're right, I did,"],[3858,4008,"I did save your dad's life."],[4008,4095,"You what?"],[4095,4275,"Grace saved your dad's life?"],[4354,4508,"If she's telling the truth,"],[4612,4713,"wouldn't that make her"],[4713,4800,"the Warlord Queen?"]],"43":[[266,479,"Are you shitting me, Kevin?"],[538,754,"How the hell could a dirt-poor janitor"],[754,959,"be the freaking Warlord Queen?"],[1021,1146,"Forget it, Stella."],[1209,1305,"Don't waste your breath"],[1305,1401,"trying to make sense of this"],[1401,1547,"lunatic's bullshit."],[1593,1801,"First of all, I am not a lunatic."],[1856,1989,"I am someone you all should be grateful"],[1989,2131,"you're even sharing a room with."],[2185,2352,"Second of all, I do know Stella's dad-"],[2352,2444,"Okay, enough."],[2640,2786,"You're right, Grace."],[2836,2969,"You're not a lunatic."],[3019,3144,"Because you make lunatics"],[3144,3382,"look like goddamn geniuses!"],[4108,4204,"Sure,"],[4262,4329,"you might've gotten"],[4329,4454,"straight-A's in school."],[4454,4587,"You might have outscored us"],[4587,4746,"on all those tests."],[4779,4946,"But look at you now."],[5000,5201,"You're just a stinky little janitor"],[5201,5413,"who cleans the same toilets we shit in."],[5613,5809,"Get it through your head, Grace."],[5809,5930,"You're a nobody."],[5930,6089,"You're no better than the filth"],[6089,6289,"you scrub out of those toilets."],[6331,6431,"I won't take this again."],[6519,6639,"You keep Grace's name."],[6639,6740,"out of your mouth!"]],"44":[[116,304,"What, I can't call a spade a spade?"],[371,538,"Grace, you're trash."],[538,721,"You're a fucking nobody."],[721,992,"Fraudulent, lying, psycho-ass bitch."],[1755,1864,"You bitch!"],[1864,1935,"Ah!"],[2102,2168,"Ah!"],[2427,2548,"Ahhhh!"],[3153,3194,"Well?"],[3290,3361,"Anyone else have anything"],[3361,3470,"they'd like to add?"],[3645,3828,"Grace, are you out of your mind?"],[3828,3924,"I tried to tell you,"],[3924,4170,"Stella's dad is a very powerful man."],[4170,4233,"Oh, yeah?"],[4233,4291,"Once he finds out"],[4291,4391,"what you did to his daughter,"],[4391,4529,"he's gonna destroy you."],[4600,4758,"Well, I'd like to see how he's going to"],[4838,4917,"destroy me."],[4959,5034,"Alright, hey, but you're"],[5034,5167,"on your own this time, Grace."],[5255,5372,"Don't say I didn't warn you."],[6393,6452,"What the hell are you"],[6452,6544,"in such a rush for?"],[6544,6652,"Where's my daughter?"],[6652,6694,"Sir,"],[6694,6760,"I, I swear to God,"],[6760,6861,"I had nothing to do with this."],[6861,6977,"I didn't attack Stella."],[6994,7102,"Uh, it was Grace."],[7215,7311,"There was so much blood."],[7311,7457,"Someone made my daughter bleed?"],[7457,7586,"Do they have a fucking death wish?"],[7586,7691,"Take me to her now!"],[7749,7845,"She's right over there."],[7845,7924,"She's over there."]],"45":[[354,500,"Alright, who the fuck"],[500,658,"did this to my daughter?"],[738,921,"Dad, what took you so long?"],[1105,1167,"Oh my God."],[1238,1359,"Darling, what happened?"],[1401,1534,"We gotta get you to the hospital."],[1534,1634,"Not yet."],[1634,1805,"I want you to make that psycho bitch"],[1805,1960,"pay for what she did to me."],[2093,2160,"Scared, Grace?"],[2160,2252,"Because you should be,"],[2252,2398,"because you're about to be crushed!"],[2473,2527,"Ugh!"],[2952,3019,"See?"],[3044,3103,"It's her!"],[3119,3253,"She's the psycho bitch."],[3253,3395,"She smashed like four bottles of wine"],[3395,3495,"over my head."],[3645,3966,"Who ever hurts my daughter is dead."],[4500,4629,"Ms. Blackwood?"]],"46":[[0,141,"Ms. Blackwood?"],[166,304,"Long time no see, Steve."],[342,412,"Kudos."],[442,575,"You have certainly raised an"],[575,729,"admirable young woman."],[884,1017,"Bullying my sister."],[1096,1259,"Calling me a psycho bitch."],[1330,1384,"She's a real sweetheart,"],[1384,1455,"isn't she?"],[1501,1655,"When you first told me about her,"],[1655,1851,"wanted her to be my assistant, this"],[1922,2177,"wasn't what I thought you had in mind."],[2177,2281,"What are you talking about,"],[2281,2444,"bullying your sister?"],[2460,2665,"God, Grace, you're seriously unhinged."],[2698,2831,"I swear my father is gonna make"],[2831,2977,"you wish you were never born!"],[3495,3591,"Dad, why would you-"],[3591,3691,"I'm so sorry, ma'am."],[3691,3795,"All of this is my fault."],[3795,3908,"What the hell are you saying?"],[3908,3966,"Shut up!"],[4012,4145,"Tell her you're sorry this instant."],[4145,4279,"Why would I tell her I'm sorry?"],[4279,4408,"She's the one that attacked me."],[4450,4575,"If she attacked you,"],[4575,4671,"you must have done something"],[4671,4771,"truly unforgivable!"],[4771,4875,"What are you talking about?"],[4904,5055,"She's not a power player anymore,"],[5055,5255,"her company just went bankrupt."],[5276,5513,"All she is a dirt-poor cleaning lady."],[5547,5714,"A slutty, home-wrecking"],[5714,5839,"cleaning lady at that!"],[5930,6072,"Do you even hear yourself right now?"],[6110,6177,"Bankrupt?"],[6202,6385,"How the fuck could she be bankrupt?"],[6385,6523,"If she's bankrupt,"],[6523,6652,"then this entire country"],[6652,6748,"is in a recession!"]],"47":[[4,120,"What are you talking about?"],[141,216,"How can a janitor"],[216,396,"influence the domestic economy?"],[396,517,"That doesn't make any sense!"],[558,684,"Apologize this instant,"],[684,817,"or you'll drag our entire"],[817,892,"extended family"],[892,1013,"to this mess you've created."],[1013,1180,"Jesus, what is going on with you, Dad?"],[1180,1443,"You are Steve fucking Sterling,"],[1443,1630,"a hotel luxury owner."],[1685,1764,"You are friends with"],[1764,1889,"the Warlord Queen."],[1951,2135,"Why are you being so generous to this"],[2135,2289,"trash-sweeping clown?"],[2314,2498,"Who the hell are you calling a"],[2498,2660,"trash-sweeping clown?"],[3011,3165,"Oh, it's Mr. Cohen."],[3294,3495,"Oh, fuck me, he's hot."],[3524,3649,"That's Mr. Cohen?"],[3757,3807,"Then..."],[3895,3966,"who's that lady"],[3966,4079,"standing next to him?"],[4137,4237,"Stella."],[4371,4504,"Is that Grace?"],[4504,4621,"Of course, I am."],[4667,4788,"Who else would I be?"],[4788,4938,"Jesus Christ!"],[4971,5084,"We've had the wrong person"],[5084,5217,"this whole time!"],[5534,5726,"But, but who is she?"]],"48":[[16,116,"But who is she?"],[200,287,"Who's she?"],[392,600,"She's the woman who saved my life."],[642,763,"She's the woman that Mr. Cohen"],[763,905,"has to be careful around."],[938,1121,"She's the woman that has this entire"],[1121,1247,"country in a vice grip!"],[1292,1551,"She's the goddamn Warlord Queen!"],[1793,1872,"What?"],[2844,2982,"You alright, Sis?"],[3036,3123,"I'm fine."],[3236,3361,"Ms. Blackwood,"],[3390,3516,"this is all my fault."],[3528,3728,"It's all because of my awful parenting."],[3774,3845,"I just asked that"],[3845,3937,"you show some restraint"],[3937,4041,"and, and don't hold us against"],[4041,4129,"my daughter."],[4179,4316,"I give you my word I'll see to it"],[4316,4491,"that she's disciplined for her actions."],[4571,4650,"I'm so sorry."],[4775,4850,"I didn't know you were the"],[4850,4954,"Warlord Queen."]],"49":[[133,275,"Grace, why, why don't you just"],[275,412,"tell your sister to let it go?"],[517,558,"Yeah, Grace,"],[558,688,"we didn't mean any harm by it."],[688,934,"It was just a simple misunderstanding."],[963,1117,"Oh, so"],[1159,1280,"now that you know who she is,"],[1280,1401,"you're begging for my help?"],[1488,1589,"That's funny,"],[1614,1714,"cause it was crickets"],[1714,1889,"when she was abusing my sister."],[1935,2039,"Ms. Blackwood,"],[2106,2223,"should I handle them for you?"],[2223,2410,"Ma'am, um, please, we, we messed up."],[2410,2523,"It won't happen again."],[2523,2731,"Yeah, it was all Stella's fault."],[2731,2857,"She made us believe that"],[2857,2990,"you were something you are not."],[3365,3495,"Worshiping the strong,"],[3541,3653,"bullying the weak."],[3737,3849,"You know, I never would've guessed"],[3849,4020,"that you graduated from one of the top"],[4058,4179,"high schools in the country."],[4208,4383,"Thousands spent on tuition,"],[4429,4583,"and not a single one of you"],[4583,4771,"was able to learn basic empathy."],[4959,5088,"You know, you all should be ashamed"],[5088,5171,"that you call yourselves"],[5171,5267,"Americans."]],"50":[[158,258,"Listen up."],[325,508,"If I hear any of you"],[546,684,"so much as whisper"],[713,971,"my sister's name ever again,"],[1105,1259,"I will make you suffer"],[1463,1651,"more than you ever could imagine."],[2052,2122,"Let's go."],[3140,3207,"Ladies, wait."],[3282,3395,"I'm signing a contract with a"],[3395,3507,"business partner tonight."],[3536,3645,"There's gonna be a banquet,"],[3682,3820,"lots of big names attending."],[3878,4037,"I'd love it if you both could make it."],[4517,4600,"Milo Blackwood?"],[4617,4708,"Oh, do you know him?"],[4808,4925,"I know you guys had the same last name,"],[4925,5080,"I just thought it was a coincidence."],[5080,5150,"It's Dad."],[5205,5284,"We should go."],[5434,5534,"I, I know how you feel"],[5534,5684,"about everything, but..."],[5809,5897,"Aside from you,"],[5897,6076,"he's the only family I have."],[6206,6277,"We're not going."],[6385,6448,"What?"]],"51":[[41,95,"What?"],[95,191,"Everything that happened"],[191,287,"is in the past."],[287,396,"Maybe he's different."],[396,583,"Maybe he's changed."],[600,754,"We won't know unless we go."],[1326,1472,"Grace, I found food."],[1776,1935,"It's Daddy!"],[2781,2898,"What the hell are you doing,"],[2898,3040,"you filthy beggar!"],[3040,3157,"God, you stink."],[3194,3361,"Now beat it before your sewer"],[3361,3499,"smell gets onto my son."],[3666,3866,"Daddy, why did you do that?"],[3874,3995,"She's your daughter."],[3995,4091,"We both are."],[4112,4191,"Daughters?"],[4254,4425,"The only child I have is my only son,"],[4425,4508,"Brian, here."],[4571,4683,"You're nothing but a couple of dirty,"],[4683,4821,"street rats."],[5196,5276,"Oh."],[5276,5426,"Hey, stop!"],[5426,5526,"Oh, great."],[5584,5714,"Got that right, honey."],[6126,6222,"Grace, I have given him"],[6222,6348,"chance after chance,"],[6348,6431,"and he has let us down"],[6431,6552,"every single time."],[6552,6664,"I have given up hope for him"],[6664,6735,"coming back."],[6777,6919,"Look, the only thing that I care about"],[6919,7032,"is your happiness."],[7278,7328,"Yep."],[7399,7453,"Boss,"],[7494,7582,"the custom-made dress"],[7582,7720,"you requested is ready."],[7799,7874,"Okay, I'll be there."],[8020,8108,"Alright, well, I have to go."],[8237,8291,"Thomas,"],[8291,8441,"thank you for the invitation, but"],[8462,8596,"we're gonna skip the banquet tonight."],[8633,8717,"Uh, no worries."],[8742,8833,"I understand."],[8913,9009,"You stay here,"],[9009,9042,"and I'll come back"],[9042,9142,"and get you later, okay?"],[9184,9259,"Alright."],[9797,9889,"Sorry, Cat."],[9972,10105,"I'm going to that banquet."],[10176,10385,"If Dad's really forgotten us,"],[10447,10631,"I need to see it for myself."]],"52":[[800,900,"There he is."],[967,1046,"Proud of you, son."],[1046,1126,"Your new company's"],[1126,1213,"barely up and running,"],[1213,1334,"and you're already closing deals"],[1334,1418,"with Thomas Cohen."],[1434,1572,"Big things ahead for you, bud."],[1572,1618,"Oh."],[1618,1822,"Milo, aren't you just over the moon"],[1822,1997,"about how well Brian's doing?"],[2014,2185,"I mean, he's eons better than those"],[2185,2356,"street trash daughters of yours."],[2398,2510,"They're not my daughters."],[2606,2706,"They're dead to me."],[2819,2936,"You know how I'm a huge fan"],[2936,3069,"of the Warlord Queen, right?"],[3128,3228,"I heard someone say"],[3253,3415,"she was gonna be attending tonight."],[3457,3557,"Just think"],[3557,3737,"if she sees my company's potential,"],[3737,3887,"she might even invest!"],[3887,4074,"It's practically a done deal."],[4074,4129,"Hmm."],[4129,4241,"I heard through the grapevine"],[4241,4387,"that Mr. Cohen personally"],[4387,4517,"invited the Warlord Queen"],[4517,4617,"to attend our banquet."],[4617,4758,"No freaking way!"],[4942,5084,"The Warlord Queen,"],[5121,5251,"someone of her stature."],[5305,5459,"Would she really make time"],[5459,5572,"for people like us?"],[5572,5739,"You're a hotshot CEO now."],[5751,5855,"Better get used to it."],[5855,5968,"Stay here, okay?"],[5997,6068,"I'm gonna go double check"],[6068,6210,"with Mr. Cohen right now."],[6531,6614,"Grace."],[6823,6902,"What are you doing here?"],[6944,7140,"So we're dead to you, huh?"]],"53":[[129,216,"Oh God."],[233,321,"Not this again."],[362,425,"Listen."],[471,717,"First, you two share the same DNA"],[717,846,"as your bitch of a mother."],[846,1021,"Second, you're cursed!"],[1109,1222,"You're walking goddamn"],[1222,1347,"bad luck charms."],[1405,1514,"Since the day you were born,"],[1514,1689,"I haven't caught a goddamn break."],[1739,1843,"And you expect me to have some"],[1843,2102,"sort of parental affection for you?"],[2268,2423,"Catherine said you abused us."],[2519,2615,"You would get drunk."],[2640,2748,"You would hit her."],[2748,2852,"And you would yell at me."],[2932,3057,"Then when I was four years old,"],[3057,3286,"you left us out on the street."],[3395,3541,"Was that not enough, Dad?"],[3716,3787,"Do you have to"],[3816,4033,"humiliate us as adults now, too?"],[4099,4212,"I'm your father!"],[4316,4408,"Humiliate you?"],[4437,4512,"Hit you?"],[4529,4708,"I'll do whatever I goddamn please!"],[4729,4867,"Fathers don't hit."],[4963,5050,"They don't yell."],[5050,5213,"They don't abuse."],[5380,5451,"They love."],[5513,5618,"If you can't do that,"],[5663,5834,"then you don't deserve"],[5834,5951,"to be our father."]],"54":[[4,95,"Think you can talk back"],[95,225,"just because you're grown up now?"],[246,408,"Goddamn bastard child."],[442,529,"You seeing this?"],[617,692,"My daughter showed up"],[692,813,"uninvited to our banquet,"],[829,917,"and now she's trying to"],[917,992,"pick a fight with me"],[992,1088,"in front of everyone!"],[1146,1284,"He does have a point."],[1330,1434,"You really think we wanna hear about"],[1434,1564,"your family drama?"],[1593,1718,"These Gen Z kids."],[1760,1818,"They were all a bunch of"],[1818,1918,"spoiled brats."],[1951,2068,"You've got it all wrong."],[2185,2369,"My father is a liar!"],[2481,2606,"He left my sister and I"],[2606,2723,"for a new family,"],[2798,2957,"so we made one of our own."],[3073,3324,"And we are way more successful"],[3324,3520,"than you will ever be!"],[3520,3666,"Get out of here now, Grace."],[3728,3837,"You're street trash then,"],[3837,3983,"and you're street trash now!"],[4020,4229,"My son Brian here started his own"],[4229,4396,"multi-billion dollar company."],[4462,4633,"That's what real success looks like."],[4767,4821,"Brian,"],[4888,5109,"he's a big Warlord Queen fanboy,"],[5176,5221,"right?"],[5313,5426,"Well, I will tell you"],[5538,5709,"that without explicit consent"],[5709,5826,"from my sister,"],[5826,5935,"he will never"],[5935,6051,"meet the Warlord Queen"],[6051,6239,"in his entire life!"]],"55":[[100,216,"Bravo, Grace."],[600,709,"If your sister actually"],[709,821,"knows the Warlord Queen,"],[821,1001,"I'll take back everything I said."],[1001,1067,"Happy?"],[1084,1130,"Dad,"],[1167,1405,"stop wasting your time with this loser."],[1405,1514,"The Warlord Queen"],[1514,1643,"could show up any minute."],[1643,1805,"Yeah, Milo, you're not gonna get"],[1805,1943,"anywhere with Grace."],[1943,2081,"Just forget her,"],[2081,2243,"and focus on giving a proper welcome"],[2243,2356,"to Brian's hero."],[2431,2527,"Leave it to me, kid."],[2581,2652,"I'll talk to Mr. Cohen and"],[2652,2706,"arrange for you"],[2706,2823,"to meet the Warlord Queen."],[3061,3136,"Tell you what,"],[3194,3294,"my son's closing a deal"],[3294,3395,"with CGE tonight."],[3395,3536,"Some of the most wealthiest men"],[3536,3703,"in California will be in attendance."],[3716,3820,"Why don't you go freshen up,"],[3820,3933,"and make yourself look pretty?"],[3991,4087,"When you come back,"],[4087,4195,"I'll see if I can set you up"],[4195,4295,"with somebody nice."],[4295,4416,"Get you a nice sugar daddy."],[4491,4542,"See?"],[4596,4750,"I'm not such a bad father after all."],[4917,5009,"And if that"],[5050,5192,"Warlord Queen sister of yours"],[5205,5305,"happens to be free,"],[5363,5455,"have her come by,"],[5455,5634,"and I can set her up with a man too."],[5976,6047,"Excuse me."],[6122,6210,"I heard the Warlord Queen is"],[6210,6297,"in the hotel."],[6343,6393,"Yes."],[6427,6610,"She's over there talking to Mr. Cohen."],[6660,6806,"They should be coming down soon."]],"56":[[1055,1092,"Ah!"],[1117,1222,"Fucking hell!"],[1259,1384,"Watch where you're going!"],[1722,1893,"I saw that, you bitch!"],[1926,2110,"You bumped into Brian on purpose."],[2122,2214,"Let me guess,"],[2231,2344,"you're jealous he's signing a"],[2344,2464,"fat investment contract,"],[2464,2694,"and now you wanna ruin his big night?"],[2781,2869,"Damn it, Grace."],[2869,3011,"You never fucking learn."],[3128,3324,"I did not bump into him."],[3324,3528,"Oh, so you expected us to believe that"],[3528,3678,"Brian just spilled wine"],[3678,3787,"all over himself?"],[3787,3878,"Oh, watch out, Mom."],[3878,3970,"Watch out."],[3987,4091,"Remember what she said,"],[4145,4287,"her sister is in cahoots"],[4287,4433,"with the Warlord Queen."],[4458,4587,"We need to be careful"],[4587,4738,"not to cross them."],[4800,4929,"Don't be silly, Brian."],[4975,5059,"You're signing a contract"],[5059,5142,"with Mr. Cohen,"],[5142,5259,"somebody who's actually"],[5259,5413,"seeing the Warlord Queen."],[5459,5580,"When she arrives,"],[5580,5759,"I'll ask her if she knows Grace,"],[5759,5872,"and her fraud sister."],[5976,6168,"Dad, I am trying to tell you"],[6168,6285,"that Catherine is-"],[6285,6414,"No more excuses!"],[6456,6639,"You owe Brian an apology,"],[6664,6852,"and a new suit."],[6973,7148,"I'm not gonna owe him anything."]],"57":[[50,145,"Really, Dad?"],[241,354,"You're gonna hit your daughter"],[354,500,"for telling the truth?"],[500,571,"Truth?"],[642,775,"The truth is you've been a nuisance"],[775,921,"ever since you walked in."],[1076,1172,"My son Brian"],[1172,1347,"is about to secure a deal with a man"],[1347,1518,"that made Forbes 30 under 30."],[1530,1634,"It's a once-in-a-lifetime"],[1634,1714,"opportunity."],[1714,1826,"You think he can sign"],[1826,2002,"with a wine-stained suit?"],[2047,2273,"You owe him a new suit now!"],[2727,2786,"Sergeant."],[2882,2990,"Boss, your dress is ready."],[3032,3090,"Good."],[3128,3253,"You go get the car,"],[3253,3386,"and I'm gonna get changed."],[3403,3499,"I'm gonna pick up my sister"],[3499,3578,"to take her home."],[3591,3691,"Yes, ma'am."],[3753,3807,"Dalton."],[4391,4475,"Bad news, boss."],[4533,4625,"Apparently some people"],[4625,4738,"are bullying your sister."],[4954,5042,"Take me to her."],[5192,5246,"She was already"],[5246,5326,"bullied in high school."],[5326,5442,"I'm not gonna let that happen again."],[5442,5530,"Yes, ma'am."]],"58":[[58,212,"Yes, Brian is your son."],[316,508,"But I am still your daughter!"],[508,671,"Don't you dare mention yourself"],[671,754,"in the same sentence"],[754,896,"as my precious Brian."],[946,1009,"We both know"],[1009,1188,"if it wasn't for Milo's kindness,"],[1188,1267,"you would've been kicked the"],[1267,1393,"fuck out of here already!"],[1418,1518,"That's right."],[1589,1747,"You have not changed, Grace."],[1847,2035,"You're just a filthy, orphan beggar"],[2035,2214,"that no one gives a shit about."],[2235,2298,"Dad,"],[2423,2585,"I'm giving you one last chance."],[2610,2715,"Do you really"],[2715,2865,"not see us as your daughters?"],[2911,3086,"Are we really dead to you?"],[3111,3294,"You've been dead to me since the day I"],[3294,3415,"threw you out on the street!"],[3499,3620,"Hear that, Grace?"],[3666,3837,"You're orphan scum."],[3908,4049,"Nobody fucking likes you."],[4191,4350,"Now look, my suit"],[4379,4575,"costs more than your whole life,"],[4575,4742,"so I'll go easy on you."],[4775,4950,"How about we, uh, we say you give me"],[4950,5059,"500 grand,"],[5092,5188,"and we'll call it good."],[5205,5447,"You are not getting a damn penny."],[5480,5613,"If you don't cough up the money,"],[5638,5764,"we're gonna throw you out!"],[5809,5901,"You know, I actually thought that"],[5901,6051,"maybe you had changed."],[6051,6260,"I guess I was wrong to get my hopes up."],[6297,6423,"Oh, and don't bother waiting"],[6423,6544,"for the Warlord Queen,"],[6544,6677,"because she's never coming."],[6735,6902,"And that contract with CGE,"],[6940,7061,"it's gonna be cancelled."],[7432,7549,"Not so fast."],[7628,7782,"You didn't just ruin my suit"],[7782,7899,"when you bumped into me."],[7941,8083,"You stepped on my shoe too."],[8133,8304,"Which means you're not leaving here"],[8304,8679,"until you get down and lick it clean!"]],"59":[[54,212,"I said I was sorry, Brian."],[312,367,"Drop it."],[462,700,"I'm signing with Mr. Cohen today, okay?"],[700,834,"Everybody's here for me."],[834,967,"This is my moment!"],[1051,1251,"I'll do whatever the fuck I want."],[1330,1418,"Dad, are you seriously"],[1418,1576,"gonna let them treat us like this?"],[1639,1793,"I know that you never cared"],[1793,1910,"for Catherine or I,"],[1926,2193,"but we are still your daughters!"],[2444,2498,"See?"],[2552,2681,"That's your daughter,"],[2727,2907,"disrespectful and rude."],[2944,3007,"Dad,"],[3090,3236,"this is the biggest day of my life."],[3261,3449,"Are you seriously gonna let her just"],[3507,3707,"humiliate me in front of everyone?"],[3787,3845,"Don't worry."],[3874,3974,"I'll take care of this."],[4016,4179,"I'm not gonna let anyone hurt you."],[4325,4408,"All of my life,"],[4450,4533,"you and your sister"],[4533,4662,"have been a pain in my ass."],[4704,4971,"And now, you're trying to ruin my son."],[5000,5105,"Dad, what are you doing?"],[5739,5976,"Lick Brian's boot clean!"]],"60":[[0,229,"Lick Brian's boot clean!"],[725,813,"Oh my God, look!"],[825,938,"It says the Warlord Queen's"],[938,1030,"coming tonight."],[1280,1347,"No way."],[1393,1455,"Here?"],[1480,1651,"Cat's here?"],[1705,1768,"No way."],[1768,1826,"Yeah."],[1826,1893,"Here!"],[1935,1976,"Yeah!"],[1976,2114,"I, I never thought"],[2114,2223,"that we'd have a chance"],[2223,2356,"to see her in person."],[2356,2598,"Mom, Dad, did you hear that?"],[2623,2723,"I'm finally gonna meet"],[2723,2848,"the Warlord Queen!"],[2902,3036,"She's coming here for you, son."],[3082,3219,"I'm so proud of you."],[3282,3490,"With the Warlord Queen's support,"],[3490,3699,"nothing is gonna stop us now!"],[3853,3916,"Hey."],[3970,4108,"Where do you think you're going?"],[4129,4229,"Didn't you say we,"],[4229,4396,"we couldn't meet the Warlord Queen"],[4396,4558,"without your sister's approval?"],[4608,4667,"Move."],[4721,4804,"I know her."],[4804,4879,"She's-"],[4909,5017,"Yeah, right."],[5067,5301,"Like you'd ever know the Warlord Queen."],[5321,5459,"You're not going anywhere."],[5518,5601,"Tonight,"],[5601,5747,"you're gonna keep the guests happy."],[5830,6147,"Do that, and maybe I'll set you up"],[6147,6297,"with a few rich guys."]],"61":[[16,129,"No, thanks."],[329,392,"Oh!"],[392,513,"Ungrateful bitch!"],[513,588,"Stop pretending"],[588,675,"you're better than this."],[675,754,"Look around."],[788,892,"These are the richest people"],[892,1013,"in California."],[1013,1130,"If you just play along,"],[1130,1267,"you might actually get"],[1267,1384,"something out of it!"],[1384,1451,"See that?"],[1476,1655,"My wife and son are way too nice."],[1655,1760,"They're giving you a chance to"],[1760,1860,"turn your life around."],[2006,2118,"Drop the act."],[2156,2289,"Just tell me who you want."],[2314,2498,"You're my dad's daughter."],[2498,2702,"I'll bend the rules for you."],[2998,3148,"I don't want any of this."],[3148,3253,"I said no!"],[3253,3340,"Oh, fuck!"],[3386,3445,"Oh."],[3661,3795,"You little bitch!"],[3824,4008,"How dare you push me!"],[4029,4183,"I'll strip off everything and"],[4183,4404,"show everybody what you really are!"],[4404,4512,"Wait, no."],[4512,4642,"No, let me go!"],[4642,4725,"Stop!"],[4817,4904,"No, please!"],[4946,5046,"No."],[5238,5313,"Stop!"],[5714,5843,"Let go of me!"],[6669,6815,"Let go of my sister."],[6881,6944,"Now!"]],"62":[[454,517,"What?"],[1297,1430,"Don't worry, I'll handle this."],[1555,1689,"Did you just kick me?"],[1743,1805,"Catherine, you're a"],[1876,1943,"janitor?"],[2060,2214,"Look what your daughter did to me."],[2248,2406,"She actually kicked me!"],[2464,2515,"Catherine,"],[2515,2665,"have you lost your fucking mind?"],[2665,2831,"You do not ever touch my sister"],[2831,3103,"ever again, or I will make you pay!"],[3232,3299,"Look at you."],[3328,3445,"Nothing but a janitor."],[3465,3591,"It's a good thing I left you,"],[3607,3707,"and your sister."],[3978,4137,"You're gonna regret saying that."],[4137,4233,"Are you kidding me?"],[4270,4454,"Do you even know where you are?"],[4454,4546,"What makes you think"],[4546,4683,"you can touch my mom?"],[4771,4867,"And you are?"],[4867,4963,"That's my son."],[5038,5196,"Everyone's here to see the deal"],[5196,5359,"he made with Mr. Cohen."],[5380,5559,"And you two have done nothing"],[5559,5689,"but embarrass me."],[5689,5805,"One of you is a moron,"],[5805,5851,"and the other"],[5851,5980,"doesn't have any manners."],[5989,6114,"You made me look like a fool."],[6239,6352,"Who cares?"],[6352,6423,"The day that you"],[6423,6510,"stepped out of that door"],[6510,6623,"left Grace and I,"],[6669,6781,"was the day that you stopped"],[6781,6886,"being our father."],[6936,7152,"How dare you talk to my dad like that!"],[7603,7649,"Bitch!"],[7649,7778,"Are you crazy?"],[8003,8078,"Oh!"]],"63":[[16,175,"You little bastards!"],[175,287,"How dare you!"],[287,450,"You can't talk to us like this."],[475,550,"Oh, what are you gonna"],[550,638,"do about it, huh?"],[667,775,"All you ever do is whine and"],[775,867,"play the victim."],[867,1109,"And you're nothing but a filthy janitor."],[1384,1526,"Did you just hit me?"],[1526,1693,"You're damn right, I did."],[1760,1864,"And I'll do it again."],[1914,2089,"Milo, look at your daughters!"],[2110,2235,"You're just gonna sit there,"],[2235,2377,"and let them throw us around like that?"],[2377,2460,"Do something!"],[2515,2602,"You little-"],[2769,2852,"Ah!"],[2927,2986,"You're hurting me!"],[2986,3090,"I'm your father!"],[3165,3290,"You should've thought of that"],[3290,3486,"before you left us, walked out."],[3953,4087,"You're gonna pay for this."],[4087,4237,"When the Warlord Queen gets here,"],[4237,4375,"you guys are screwed!"],[4479,4583,"If they only knew,"],[4654,4829,"I'm the Warlord Queen."],[5839,5972,"Who's causing trouble at my event?"]],"64":[[41,129,"Is that Mr. Cohen?"],[129,291,"Is, isn't Mr. Cohen"],[291,467,"meant to be with the Warlord Queen?"],[492,596,"Where is she?"],[638,734,"Brian, look."],[788,917,"The Warlord Queen's men."],[1330,1430,"Mr. Cohen."],[1455,1601,"Oh my gosh, it's so good to see you."],[1601,1785,"So, am I finally gonna get to"],[1785,1956,"meet the Warlord Queen?"],[2231,2318,"What's going on here?"],[2485,2581,"Don't worry about them."],[2606,2711,"Just two nobodies"],[2711,2823,"who tried to sneak in."],[2865,3048,"A janitor and some tramp."],[3078,3207,"I'll throw them out before they"],[3207,3336,"mess up the signing tonight."],[3666,3778,"Watch your mouth, idiot."],[3870,3945,"The deal's off."],[4200,4245,"Move."],[4896,5067,"Forgive us, Warlord Queen, for,"],[5167,5263,"for being late."],[5584,5822,"The Warlord Queen?"],[5864,6101,"Did Mr. Cohen just call that bitch"],[6101,6260,"the Warlord Queen?"],[6485,6544,"Shut up!"],[6635,6735,"This is the Warlord Queen."],[6806,6902,"Show your respect."]],"65":[[50,221,"My daughter is the Warlord Queen."],[342,437,"The one who controls"],[437,592,"all the special agents across the world."],[1384,1468,"Grace,"],[1584,1714,"I know this is sudden."],[1785,1918,"But since the moment I saw you,"],[2047,2160,"I knew you were the one."],[2318,2402,"Will you marry me?"],[2548,2744,"This is so sudden."],[2802,2923,"I, I know your sister"],[2923,3044,"is the Warlord Queen,"],[3061,3290,"and you're way out of my league, but,"],[3390,3578,"if you give me a chance,"],[3657,3753,"I'll spend the rest of my life"],[3753,3849,"proving myself."],[4466,4558,"Hand me the gift."],[4800,4992,"We're shifting all of Brian's contracts"],[4992,5092,"to your company."],[5359,5722,"I'm also giving you 20% share of CGE."],[5801,6118,"20% of CGE shares?"],[6218,6431,"Do you know how much that's worth?"],[6581,6806,"Thomas, I, I really appreciate this,"],[6806,7023,"but I can build"],[7023,7169,"my company on my own."],[7244,7415,"This is too much to ask."],[7494,7586,"It's nothing compared to"],[7586,7711,"what your sister's done for you."]],"66":[[4,108,"Grace, we can't choose"],[108,187,"where we're born,"],[266,408,"or who our parents are."],[508,633,"No matter the hardships that life"],[633,725,"throws at us,"],[779,913,"I will always prove"],[950,1138,"that you and I are one of a kind."],[1259,1413,"As long as I have you,"],[1534,1643,"I have enough."],[1835,1931,"Go on, Tommy."],[2348,2527,"Six billion dollars shall be transferred"],[2527,2652,"to Grace Blackwood"],[2652,2794,"as an engagement gift."],[2857,2961,"Catherine."],[3232,3278,"Don't cry."],[3278,3378,"You're gonna ruin your makeup."],[4512,4596,"Okay, that's enough."],[4767,4867,"I want them out of here."],[5221,5380,"Tonight is for me and my sister."],[5547,5609,"Catherine,"],[5663,5768,"you can't do this to me."],[5826,5939,"I'm your father."],[6101,6243,"Grace, trust me."],[6268,6402,"I've always loved you both."],[6448,6639,"You left us when we had nothing,"],[6639,6798,"and now that we're worth something,"],[6798,6886,"you want us back?"],[6911,7069,"What kind of father does that?"],[7102,7169,"Grace,"],[7273,7353,"please!"],[7515,7611,"I was wrong!"],[7753,7857,"I'll make it right."],[8033,8162,"You asshole!"],[8224,8350,"How could you just run back"],[8350,8500,"to your daughters like that?"],[8500,8608,"What about me?"],[8629,8783,"What about our son?"]],"67":[[200,329,"If it wasn't for you,"],[329,462,"I never would have left them."],[479,621,"I could've been a billionaire,"],[621,813,"and the Warlord Queen's father."],[850,959,"This is all your fault."],[1217,1434,"Don't you dare blame me!"],[1484,1543,"You were the one"],[1543,1639,"who called your daughters"],[1639,1751,"ungrateful and useless."],[1751,1926,"You begged me for a son."],[1951,2014,"And now,"],[2014,2110,"your daughters have power,"],[2110,2260,"you're turning on me?"],[3078,3153,"Go on,"],[3186,3265,"take them."],[3653,3724,"Let go off me. - No."],[3787,3853,"Let go!"],[3962,4033,"No!"]],"68":[[216,275,"It's over."],[417,554,"They can't hurt us ever again."],[633,688,"So,"],[754,917,"about what I asked earlier,"],[1005,1134,"I'm still waiting for an answer."],[1497,1785,"Yes, I'll marry you."],[6385,6531,"Alright, let me get one with two of you."],[6815,7111,"Three, two, one, smile!"]]}